1. From Boot Loader menu pass parameter to kernel

linux /boot/vmlinuz-version root=UUID=hex ro quite init=/bin/bash

2.
Remount your root file system in read/write mode
mount -o remount,rw /
3.
Change passwword
passwd
4. Synchronization
sync
reboot
